# Project: Alberto Marchiorello — Web Design Business Website

This is a **lead generation and client acquisition website** for Alberto's web design & development freelance business. The goal is to attract customers and sell custom website builds. It is NOT a personal portfolio — it is a business/service website.

## Purpose
- Generate leads from businesses, brands, and founders who need a website
- Showcase services, process, and past work to convert visitors into paying clients
- Offer a consultation/intake flow powered by AI

## Key facts
- **Owner/Builder:** Alberto Marchiorello (goes by "Albi")
- **Live URL:** https://marchio.design
- **Vercel project:** `website-builder` under `menoguds-projects`
- **GitHub repo:** https://github.com/MeNoGud/Website-Bilder
- **Stack:** Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v3, Framer Motion

## Project structure
- All site content (name, bio, services, process steps, etc.) lives in `src/lib/site.ts` — edit there first
- Components are in `src/components/`
- Pages are in `src/app/`
- Design tokens and global styles are in `tailwind.config.ts` and `src/app/globals.css`

## Sections (in page order)
1. Hero
2. Marquee strip
3. Stats
4. Expertise (Services) — sticky scroll, `id="services"`
5. Process (How it works) — auto-scrolling carousel, `id="process"`
6. Work (Portfolio) — project cards grid, `id="work"`
7. LogoStrip
8. CallToAction
9. Contact

## Deploy
- Push to `main` on GitHub → Vercel auto-deploys to production
- Manual deploy: `vercel --prod` from the project root
